{"word":"κράζω","slug":"κράζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰράζω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κραυγή\">κραυγή</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘utter a loud cry’, <b>scream, cry out <a href='B:480 5:5'>Mk 5:5</a>; <a href='B:480 9:26'>9:26</a>; <a href='B:480 15:39'>15:39</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:490 9:39'>Lk 9:39</a>; <a href='B:730 12:2'>Rv 12:2</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘express <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> with vigorous voice’, <b>call out <a href='B:470 15:23'>Mt 15:23</a>; <a href='B:510 7:60'>Ac 7:60</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> reinforced (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a></el>) <el>φωνῇ μεγάλῃ</el> in a loud voice <b><a href='B:470 27:50'>Mt 27:50</a>; <a href='B:510 7:57'>Ac 7:57</a>; <a href='B:730 6:10'>Rv 6:10</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> In <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense: of inner utterance <b><a href='B:520 8:15'>Ro 8:15</a>; <a href='B:550 4:6'>Gal 4:6</a>;</b> of deep prophetic feeling underlying a statement <b><a href='B:520 9:27'>Ro 9:27</a>;</b> of things delivering a compelling message, stones <b><a href='B:490 19:40'>Lk 19:40</a>;</b> workers’ wages <b><a href='B:660 5:4'>Js 5:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κράβαττος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κραιπάλη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}